<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="55" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1590,2013]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1737,1762]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">Description.</emphasis>
Body length 
<quantity box="[498,601,1737,1761]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.39" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" unit="mm" value="1.39">1.39 mm</quantity>
, maximum width of elytra 
<quantity box="[911,1015,1737,1761]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.8999999999999995" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" unit="mm" value="0.59">0.59 mm</quantity>
, whole body, except posterior part of head, shiny, reddish brown, posterior part of head matt, legs and antennae yellowish brown. Head 
<number box="[1284,1333,1773,1797]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.15">1.15</number>
times as long as wide, terminal antennomere about 
<number box="[623,658,1809,1833]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.5">1.5</number>
times as long as wide, with dense, long setae. Pronotum 
<number box="[1290,1339,1809,1833]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.33">1.33</number>
times as long as head and about 
<number box="[418,467,1845,1869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.65">1.65</number>
times as wide as long. Elytra about 
<number box="[879,928,1845,1869]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="1.25">1.25</number>
times as long as abdomen, composite tergite (IV–VI) 
<number box="[250,285,1881,1905]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55" value="5.4">5.4</number>
times as long as tergites VII–VIII together, tergite VIII slightly longer than VII.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1590,2013]" box="[199,608,1917,1941]" pageId="4" pageNumber="55">Sexual dimorphism. Male unknown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
